#. <section class="sutta" id="sn31.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn31.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 31"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 31"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn31.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Gandhabbavagga"
msgstr "1. Fairies"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 3. Mūlagandhadātāsutta → mūlagandhasuttaṃ (bj) | dātā 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn31.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Mūlagandhadātāsutta"
msgstr "3. A Giver of Fragrant Roots"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.251"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn31.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā mūlagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why someone, when their body "
"breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the gods of fairykind "
"who live in fragrant roots?”"

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Idha, bhikkhu, ekacco kāyena sucaritaṃ carati, vācāya sucaritaṃ carati, "
"manasā sucaritaṃ carati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, it’s when someone does good things by way of body, speech, and "
"mind."

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.5"
msgid "Tassa sutaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "And they’ve heard:"

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.6"
msgid "‘mūlagandhe adhivatthā devā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The gods of fairykind who live in fragrant roots are long-lived, beautiful, "
"and very happy.’"

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.7"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "They think:"

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā mūlagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ "
"sahabyataṃ upapajjeyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the "
"company of the gods of fairykind who live in fragrant roots!’"

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.9"
msgid "So dātā hoti mūlagandhānaṃ."
msgstr "They give gifts of fragrant roots."

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.10"
msgid ""
"So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā mūlagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the company of the "
"gods of fairykind who live in fragrant roots."

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu … pe …"
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why someone, when their body breaks "
"up, after death, is reborn in the company of the gods of fairykind who live "
"in fragrant roots.”"

msgctxt "sn31.3:1.12"
msgid ""
"yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā mūlagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ "
"sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn31.3:1.13"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
